summary: A Large Underground thieves hideout which you can travel to all the major cities the stealthy way. It has all you could want and more.
descriptionHtml:
A large underground thieves hideout which you can use to travel outside of all the major settlements. This mod comes with vendors, blacksmith area, alchemy area, display cases/mannequins and bards. I thought it would be a cool idea to have a small underground town dedicated to the Thieves Guild. I hope you all enjoy this mod!

This mod is fully navmeshed.

No DLC required.

Feedback and comments are always appreciated!
author: itsfly
